review.comments:
Pros:
-right by the subway/bus (metro stations) 
-comfortable sleeping arrangements 
-had a kitchen we could cook our own breakfast (any meal) in
-the shower was great with warm water
-got the whole apartment to ourselves
-definitely worth it for the value we paid
-had towels and extra blankets laid out for us
-easy to get ahold of and communicate with
-free wifi

Cons:
-a little further from the city by metro than we planned
-neighbors constantly smoked weed we could smell in the apartment 
-the apartment was very hot most of the time 
-skeptical about the neighborhood

Overall, I would recommend for the value we paid.
